extendedInfo.description: High Intensity Flashlight -- A real flashlight! Not just a bright screen.This turns on your camera's LED light for use as a bright flashlight. Simple as that.Features allow you to turn the screen black or see a live feed from the camera (great for seeing into small places).Use it as a viewfinder also.Add a shortcut to your home screen for quick access.CAUTION: Strobe lighting can trigger seizures in photosensitive epilepsy!Keywords:flashlight android, torch, led flash light, strobe, brightest, El feneri, torcia, best appIn order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application.This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service.Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps.You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you.

reviews.title: Look elsewhere
reviews.comment: This app turns your light on witha simple click,,, then right back off so you can get mugged or snakebit while you fight to get rid of a bullshit ad. Look elsewhere!
reviews.author: Bill Gerwig
